name: Carty's Delivery
description:
Become a typing expert

Help Carty the minecart do his gold deliveries by practicing your typing skills! With the help of your magic keyboard, type the words you see on the screen before they fall through the red line in under a one minute timer. The more words you type, the more words will spawn!

Choose between 3 different maps: Forest, Snow and Desert. Maps do not change the gameplay in anyway, but it is still a fun thing to do and discover.

Big giant thanks to Extrinity for the music!!! Very much appreciated!!

Made for Mini Jam 85 in under 3 days
